description: TerraNet Holding AB engages in patented software technology that enables intelligent machine-to-machine communication and streaming of data, including bandwidth-demanding HD media, regardless of mobile networks or other hotspot-dependent networks. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane and currently employs 10 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-05-30. The firm delivers mobile telephony and data services via a peer-to-peer mobile mesh network of handsets and light infrastructure.
name: Terranet AB
